de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface WireType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WireTypeImpl

    public interface WireType
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Wire Type'. The properties common to all instance of a wire type

    The following features are supported:

    • Specific Weight
    • Specific Price
    • NConductors
    • Min Bending Radius
    • NShields
    • Mtbf
    See Also:
    LibraryPackage.getWireType()
